{
  "stem": "11274.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So that's why we were in the men's camp, and they divided it with that wall.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Then they took the wall away, and if remained a men's camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And block 11 was the block of death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That's where they were making all the executions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "While I was still in block 10, I heard shooting through the window.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I was just on this bunk bed, where the window was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the window was boarded up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "This was on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was boarded up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I looked through the-- to the-- openings between the window, and I saw on the wall opposite me, I saw soldiers standing in green uniforms, holding their hands like this.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then I heard the bullet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Germans were standing under my window.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't see them, the SS.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I saw the soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I discovered-- I think, these must be the uniforms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I asked later on, and the-- through the window-- shouted to him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he threw me a note.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, yes, that was. 12,000 of them were here. 7,000 are already dead, and you are wearing their uniforms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And 5,000 are particularly in block 11, shooting them every single day and killing them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's how I found out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we went to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then in Birkenau were those shelves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were six first, but so many transports were coming in every single day, we ended up with 12 of us, instead of in the length, hanging the-- feet hanging down, and just-- then just with a rag of a blanket.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was-- we came in in March.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was September-- either September or October.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "September or October, the same year.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
